messages.subject: Re: tofu
messages.messageBody:
<<<<What about "Not Chicken Nuggets"? I actually like
those better than
boca
nuggets but they are harder to find.
They also make "Not Corn Dogs" Totally gross.
Elissa, who will soon be singing
Yippee - Kai - Yay!>>>>

I've never seen those. I'll keep a look out. Tamzin
and I have tried EVERY single veggie dog type thing on
the market over here. IourHO, they are all YUCKY! In
fact, I'm feeling a bit envious of her at the moment
because she went to see her dad in the UK yesterday
for 3 weeks and she will be eating lots of YUMMY
veggie dogs.
On that note (that I've got time on my hands for 3
weeks)...I went and saw The Count of Monte Cristo
tonight (the movie, that is). I loved it! All that
period clothing and swashbuckling stuff. The lead guy
is gorgeous!! I want to dream about him tonight :-)

Meghan
